.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aMusicxPolitical aspects. 0aMusicxSocial aspects. 4aCommunication : Political Communication. 4aPhilosophy : Feminist Philosophy. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Theory. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Feminism & Feminist Theory.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780791481240?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791481240423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791481240/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles